## UML Database Model

Added the UML class diagram for the Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS) showing the main entities and their relationships:

- Lecturer- submits claims for approval.
- Claim - contains claim lines and attachments.
- Claim Attachment- stores uploaded supporting documents.
- Claim Line - details hourly work and rates.
- Approval Record - tracks approvals by Programme Coordinators and Academic Managers.
- Claim Status - maintains an audit trail of claim status changes.
